{"type": "article", "id": 22325, "title": "木桩蜡烛包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-16T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141149E6lsSxKiMUFc23az.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是澳大利亚的一家专做蜡烛的品牌  Black Arrow Candles 的蜡烛包装，外形像一个被切过的木桩，上下有年轮一样的线条，四周有潮湿纹路的痕迹。他们宣称蜡烛是从大豆中提取原料，很天然，包装上也呼应了天然的特征。设计方 THINK Packaging 从罗宾汉射中木桩的原型中找到灵感，要从中一剖为二打开，带玻璃杯的蜡烛就镶嵌在了中心，有珍贵之意。<a href=\"http://blackarrowcandles.com.au/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141147P6kwpVhdjsMiYmIa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141148QNVU358hlTEHX9Ak.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141148cxMSsp34qRrvwguA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141149aMvYAg4qePkhp7Z6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}